"title": "4834: light, natural",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4834",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Scripture stresses that every source of light (sun, moon and stars) is created by God, and subject to him.</p>\n<h2>God is the source of natural light</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:3-Gen1:5\">GEN 1:3–1:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:14-Gen1:18\">GEN 1:14–1:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:13-2Sam22:15\">2SA 22:13–22:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job41:18-Job41:21\">JOB 41:18–41:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps8:3-Ps8:4\">PSA 8:3–8:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps74:16\">PSA 74:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps97:4\">PSA 97:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps136:7-Ps136:9\">PSA 136:7–136:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa45:7\">ISA 45:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:35\">JER 31:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:17\">JAS 1:17</a></p>\n<h2>God controls natural light</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:19\">PSA 104:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job9:7\">JOB 9:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job36:30-Job36:32\">JOB 36:30–36:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps121:5-Ps121:6\">PSA 121:5–121:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:45\">MAT 5:45</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:6\">2CO 4:6</a></p>\n<h2>Miracles involving natural light</h2>\n<h3>The pillars of cloud and fire</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod13:21-Exod13:22\">EXO 13:21–13:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod14:20\">EXO 14:20</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut1:31\">DEU 1:31</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:12\">NEH 9:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:19\">NEH 9:19</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:14\">PSA 78:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps105:39\">PSA 105:39</a></p>\n<h3>Other miracles</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod9:23-Exod9:24\">EXO 9:23–9:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod10:23\">EXO 10:23</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa38:8\">ISA 38:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab3:11\">HAB 3:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:44-Luke23:45\">LUK 23:44–23:45</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:3\">ACT 9:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts22:6\">ACT 22:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts22:9\">ACT 22:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts22:11\">ACT 22:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts26:13\">ACT 26:13</a></p>\n<h2>Natural light associated with angels</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt28:3\">MAT 28:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:4\">LUK 24:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts12:7\">ACT 12:7</a></p>\n<h2>Natural light used figuratively</h2>\n<h3>The sun</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev1:16\">REV 1:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:26\">ISA 30:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:25\">LUK 21:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev12:1\">REV 12:1</a></p>\n<h3>Lightning</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:29\">LUK 9:29</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt17:2\">MAT 17:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:2\">MRK 9:2</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek1:4\">EZK 1:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan10:6\">DAN 10:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos6:5\">HOS 6:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:18\">LUK 10:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke17:24\">LUK 17:24</a></p>\n<h3>Light</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:2\">PSA 104:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek1:26-Ezek1:28\">EZK 1:26–1:28</a></p>",
